column5: Only two small largemouths for me today.  did anyone find the bite really slow this weekend or was it something i was or wasn;t doing.
which lake are you fishing in the Kawartha.
find the weeds, toss some senkos
That seems to worm for all of us.
I was on Balsam for the weekend. On Saturday the fishing was great for numbers but small. On Sunday after the storm the lake was dead
